# Create and send a scheduled digest

## User can login and navigate to Digest Builder
* Navigate to Base QA site
* Click to Sign in tab
* Login with existing user "elenrushh@gmail.com"
* Go to "Digest Builder" on Menu
* Verify page title is "Digest Builder"

## User can create new digest from template
* Click "New Digest"
* Click "Create from template"
* Verify "Digest Templates" displays
* Click "My First Digest"
* Verify message "Digest created successfully" appears

## User can set schedule for Digest
* Click "Preview & Send"
* Click "Schedule For Later"
* Select "(WIB) Asia/Jakarta" for time zone
* Select "7:03pm" for time schedule
* Enter "Schedule Test" to "Subject"
* Enter "test.share0003@gmail.com" to "Add Email"
* Click "Schedule It"
* Verify message "Email scheduled successfully!" appears